      "content": "hey, so im working on this new streetwear line for my brand and i really dont want to run into any issues with cultural appropriation or looking \"fake.\" can u help me define what actually makes an aesthetic \"authentic\" to urban culture? like what are the core vibes or visual elements that define it?",
